{"tid":1476796,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"想問Admin關於連登保安問題","createTime":"2019-08-16T02:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T07:00:37.000Z","uid":118351,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7012ec059256886173bc6e0773d07949f2a2e3","tid":1476796,"uid":118351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"admin必須知道連登依家唔係淨係一個討論區咁簡單，佢係中共嘅眼中釘同埋攻擊目標，所以保安必須有世界級程度，以下係我嘅問題同建議<br />\n<br />\n1. 想問admin你係用咩hashing方法？有無salting？<br />\nHashing方面，SHA256一定已經out，PBKDF2同bcrypt理論上唔安全， 如果可以請你轉用SCrypt或Argon2<br />\n（Argon2係2015年嘅 Password Hashing Competition嘅冠軍，係依家公認最安全hashing方法，極力推薦）<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@mpreziuso/password-hashing-pbkdf2-scrypt-bcrypt-and-argon2-e25aaf41598e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40mpreziuso%2Fpassword-hashing-pbkdf2-scrypt-bcrypt-and-argon2-e25aaf41598e&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEkaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=f59c6a98\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@mpreziuso/password-hashing-pbkdf2-scrypt-bcrypt-and-argon2-e25aaf41598e</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 連登帳號只可以用學校／ISP email申請，同現實嘅帳號持有人身分掛鈎，只要有人攞到堆email，帳號持有人即刻會被起底，如果係被政府相關人士攞到手更加會影響人身安全，而且密碼可以改但email唔改得，即係話喺連登嚟講，<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">email被起底嘅嚴重程度比起密碼高一千倍</span></ins>。<br />\n我睇另一個thread啲人話你係用緊SHA256加密但無salting，請你即刻轉用上面我所提到嘅安全hashing方法同埋一定要salt<br />\n<br />\n3. admin最近出咗公告話遲啲會有2FA，請你一定<ins>唔好比人用SMS方法</ins>，因為SMS 2FA係公認極唔安全！！！更何況有電話喺個database度，電話號碼被差人起底點算？<br />\n<a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2018/08/password-breach-teaches-reddit-that-yes-phone-based-2fa-is-that-bad/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farstechnica.com%2Finformation-technology%2F2018%2F08%2Fpassword-breach-teaches-reddit-that-yes-phone-based-2fa-is-that-bad%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEkaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=840bb7e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2018/08/password-breach-teaches-reddit-that-yes-phone-based-2fa-is-that-bad/</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有請你增加Yubikey之類嘅U2F，因為U2F比TOTP （即係Google Authenticator, Microsoft Authenticator, Authy嗰啲）更安全，幾乎無可能hack到，所以<ins>Google都推薦政治團隊或受政治迫害嘅人用U2F</ins>，好多大型網站都支援U2F包括Google、Twitter仲有以保安私隱為賣點嘅各種網站如Tutanota<br />\n我建議你比人設定一個account配2~3條key，咁就唔見咗一條都唔洗驚<br />\n參考吓Google個U2F設定頁面 <a href=\"https://landing.google.com/advancedprotection/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flanding.google.com%2Fadvancedprotection%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEkaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=70ba5412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://landing.google.com/advancedprotection/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7853fea36101a8bf225b34b35094581fcb6a25f5","tid":1476796,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:47:25.000Z","msg":"原來bcrypt都唔安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街<br />\n2FA DUO Moblie點睇 我咩都唔識 但見全球唔少大專院校用緊<br />\n留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b07e21cbdbf4c153dba5fb32a5aca0cc9e780b","tid":1476796,"uid":118351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7853fea36101a8bf225b34b35094581fcb6a25f5","tid":1476796,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:47:25.000Z","msg":"原來bcrypt都唔安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街<br />\n2FA DUO Moblie點睇 我咩都唔識 但見全球唔少大專院校用緊<br />\n留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"Duo Mobile嗰啲就係TOTP，TOTP其實隻隻都差唔多，但有機會被人假冒而且部手機一比人偷咗就無得用所以我真係唔推薦受政治迫害嘅人用"},{"pid":"3c2e138910162a1924fd49a31d74dbd3ee2027fd","tid":1476796,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:03:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba48fd85e8875bff1a0899431183ed7a0a9e823d","tid"